      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FEDERAL FELIX (6) is a promising type who notched his 4th career success when too good (29.50) at this track last time. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Looks the one to beat. RATTLIN' BYE (7) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing 34 from 71 starts. Has hit the frame at her last four runs, the latest finishing third (30.00) at this track. Has a good record here including seven wins. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Well-placed to take this out. SAHARA PEARL (4) doesn't win out of turn but looks close to breaking through. Finished third (30.01) at this track last time making it three minors on end. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Bold showing expected. SUNSHINE RHONDA (3) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to make amends.",
